html:
{% set date_obj = frappe.utils.now_datetime() %}
{% set day = date_obj.day %}
{% set month = date_obj.strftime('%b') %}
{% set year = date_obj.year %}

{% set suffix = 'th' %}
{% if day % 10 == 1 and day != 11 %}
  {% set suffix = 'st' %}
{% elif day % 10 == 2 and day != 12 %}
  {% set suffix = 'nd' %}
{% elif day % 10 == 3 and day != 13 %}
  {% set suffix = 'rd' %}
{% endif %}

<p>Date : {{ "%02d"|format(day) }}<sup>{{ suffix }}</sup>-{{ month }}-{{ year }}</p>
<br>
<p>
  To,<br>
  <b>{{doc.employee_name}}.</b><br>
  #60<br>
  Krishnappa Garden<br>
  Taverekkere<br>
  570029<br>
  <b>Employee Code : GR000366</b>
</p>
<h3 style="text-align: center; text-decoration: underline;">Confirmation Letter</h3>
<br>
<p><b>Dear {{doc.salutation}}. {{doc.employee_name}},</b></p>
<br>
<p><b>Congratulations!!!</b></p>
<br>
<p>
Based on your continued good performance during the probation period, we are pleased to hereby confirm your service
with the designation <b>{{doc.designation}}</b>, with the organization. Your confirmation will be effective
from <b>
    {% set date_obj = frappe.utils.add_days(frappe.utils.now_datetime(), 1) %}
{% set day = date_obj.day %}
{% set month = date_obj.strftime('%b') %}
{% set year = date_obj.year %}

{% set suffix = 'th' %}
{% if day % 10 == 1 and day != 11 %}
  {% set suffix = 'st' %}
{% elif day % 10 == 2 and day != 12 %}
  {% set suffix = 'nd' %}
{% elif day % 10 == 3 and day != 13 %}
  {% set suffix = 'rd' %}
{% endif %}</b>{{ "%02d"|format(day) }}<sup>{{ suffix }}</sup>-{{ month }}-{{ year }}
</p>
<br>
<p>
Indifoss Analytical Pvt. Ltd. as an organization has always respected and hailed good performance. We hope you will
continue to perform better each day and help the organization scale new heights.
</p>
<br>
<p>
Wishing you all the best for all your future endeavors!!!
</p>
<br>
<p><b>For, Indifoss Analytical Pvt. Ltd.</b></p>
<br>
<p><b>Adesh Harilal Sonar<br>HR Manager</b></p>
